{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/配置Hyper-v/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<blockquote>\n<p>安装虚拟机 VMware Workstation Pro16 或 Docker 的时候，发现找不到hyper-v功能选项。window11家庭版发现无法找到hyper-v功能选项，其实这是window自动隐藏该功能，下面讲一下怎么开启hyper-v。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"打开控制面板\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%89%93%E5%BC%80%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E9%9D%A2%E6%9D%BF\" aria-label=\"打开控制面板 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>打开控制面板</h2>\n<p>首先打开控制面板，选择： 程序</p>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/16bf0daa35574cb3d583705eeec53bc4/f2793/1.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 46.621621621621614%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"1\" title=\"1\" src=\"/static/16bf0daa35574cb3d583705eeec53bc4/fcda8/1.png\" srcset=\"/static/16bf0daa35574cb3d583705eeec53bc4/12f09/1.png 148w,\n/static/16bf0daa35574cb3d583705eeec53bc4/e4a3f/1.png 295w,\n/static/16bf0daa35574cb3d583705eeec53bc4/fcda8/1.png 590w,\n/static/16bf0daa35574cb3d583705eeec53bc4/f2793/1.png 743w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<p>选择： 启用或关闭Windows功能</p>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 518px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/54d19cb9aa975ef2bdf206887810b01e/6b9fd/2.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 27.027027027027025%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"2\" title=\"2\" src=\"/static/54d19cb9aa975ef2bdf206887810b01e/6b9fd/2.png\" srcset=\"/static/54d19cb9aa975ef2bdf206887810b01e/12f09/2.png 148w,\n/static/54d19cb9aa975ef2bdf206887810b01e/e4a3f/2.png 295w,\n/static/54d19cb9aa975ef2bdf206887810b01e/6b9fd/2.png 518w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 518px) 100vw, 518px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<p>点击Hyper-V进行关闭或打开</p>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 423px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/c6d3bff14651c288d61931cb7e69fb9e/f687d/3.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 101.35135135135135%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"3\" title=\"3\" src=\"/static/c6d3bff14651c288d61931cb7e69fb9e/f687d/3.png\" srcset=\"/static/c6d3bff14651c288d61931cb7e69fb9e/12f09/3.png 148w,\n/static/c6d3bff14651c288d61931cb7e69fb9e/e4a3f/3.png 295w,\n/static/c6d3bff14651c288d61931cb7e69fb9e/f687d/3.png 423w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 423px) 100vw, 423px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<h2 id=\"如果没有发现hyper-v，解决办法如下\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0hyper-v%EF%BC%8C%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E5%8A%9E%E6%B3%95%E5%A6%82%E4%B8%8B\" aria-label=\"如果没有发现hyper v，解决办法如下 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>如果没有发现Hyper-V，解决办法如下</h2>\n<p>在Win11搜索框，PowerShell 输入 systeminfo 命令</p>\n<p>能够看到出现了很多处理器的信息，最末尾有个 Hyper-V 要求，如果四个全为 “是”，则表示支持 Hyper-V 功能</p>\n<p>桌面新建一个记事本文件，将它的后缀改成cmd或bat，复制下面的代码</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">pushd &quot;%~dp0&quot;\n \ndir /b %SystemRoot%\\servicing\\Packages\\*Hyper-V*.mum &gt;hyper-v.txt\n \nfor /f %%i in (&#39;findstr /i . hyper-v.txt 2^&gt;nul&#39;) do dism /online /norestart /add-package:&quot;%SystemRoot%\\servicing\\Packages\\%%i&quot;\n \ndel hyper-v.txt\n\nDism /online /enable-feature /featurename:Microsoft-Hyper-V-All /LimitAccess /ALL</code></pre></div>\n<p>然后，右键选择：以管理员身份运行。代码执行结束后，重启电脑就可以了。</p>","excerpt":"安装虚拟机 VMware Workstation Pro16 或 Docker 的时候，发现找不到hyper-v功能选项。window11家庭版发现无法找到hyper-v功能选项，其实这是window自动隐藏该功能，下面讲一下怎么开启hyper-v。 打开控制面板 首先打开控制…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEHyper-v/#%E6%89%93%E5%BC%80%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E9%9D%A2%E6%9D%BF\">打开控制面板</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEHyper-v/#%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0hyper-v%EF%BC%8C%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E5%8A%9E%E6%B3%95%E5%A6%82%E4%B8%8B\">如果没有发现Hyper-V，解决办法如下</a></li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/配置Hyper-v/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"配置Hyper-v","date":"Jan 14, 2023","tags":["Linux","Hyper-v"],"keywords":["Hyper-v"],"update":"Jan 01, 0001"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/配置Hyper-v/","series":[],"lastmod":"2023-01-14"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2027115977","694178885"]}